1 RULE ONE
2 JOINT SESSIONS
3 (a) The Officers of joint sessions of the Legislature shall be
4 the President of the Senate, the Speaker of the House of
5 Representatives, the President Pro Tempore of the Senate, the
6 Secretary of the Senate, and the Clerk of the House of
7 Representatives.
